<form action="/apply/image" class="form-horizontal" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <div class="form-group">
  	<div><label class="col-sm-5 control-label"><h2><b>프로젝트 페이지 개설 신청 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></h2></label> </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div><label class="col-sm-6 control-label"><h4><b>&nbsp; - 프로젝트의 메인 이미지(900X400), (270X300) 두개를 업로드해주세요</b></h4></label> </div>
  </div>

<br/><br/><br/>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label class="col-sm-4 control-label">* 이미지를 각각 하나씩 업로드 해주세요</label>
    <br/><br/>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="editor1" class="col-sm-2 control-label">메인 이미지(900X400)</label>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
    	<textarea name="editor1" id="editor1">
       </textarea>
       <script>
            CKEDITOR.replace('editor1',{
                width: 800,
                height:1,
                filebrowserUploadUrl: '/apply/image/upload1',
            });
       </script>
<br/><br/>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="editor2" class="col-sm-2 control-label">메인 이미지(270X300)</label>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
	 <textarea name="editor2" id="editor2">
        </textarea>
        <script>
            CKEDITOR.replace('editor2',{
                width: 800,
                height:1,
                filebrowserUploadUrl: '/apply/image/upload2',
            });
        </script>
<br/><br/>
      <input type="submit" class="btn btn-default" value="신청하기"/>
    </div>
  </div>
</form>

